OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain will quickly spread
OL,6,Facross the region through the morning,
OL,7,Fpersisting through much of the day.
OL,8,FRain will be heavy at times with a
OL,9,Fchance of thundery downpours in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Windy at the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will continue through
OL,13,Fthe evening and first part of the nigh
OL,14,Fwith heavy downpours at times. Rain
OL,15,Fwill gradually ease and eventually
OL,16,Fclear towards the end of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
