OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA drier start for many on
OL,6,FTuesday with some bright spells.
OL,7,FHowever, heavy scattered showers will
OL,8,Fquickly move in during the morning,
OL,9,Fwith a chance of thunder at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fspell of rain moves through on
OL,13,FWednesday, followed by heavy blustery
OL,14,Fshowers on Thursday. Drier on Friday
OL,15,Fwith some bright spells and a few
OL,16,Fshowers at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
